name: at least its not college
description:
cover art through: https://jkirchartz.com/Glitchy3bitdither/

one day, when school was ~school~ i wrote this instead of fully dissociating and/or throwing my laptop out the window. it has stuff from they don't care about us, but condensed. it does not branch. itll probably take less than five minutes. alternative names: its my trauma and ill cry if i want to, i keep screaming but they ripped my throat out, and i hate school but i think it hates me more

content warnings for: 
sexual abuse
workplace harassment
violence
trauma
being outed
general despair
